---
title: Steakhouse Pork Chops with a Creamy Shallot Pan Sauce & Lemony Green Beans
description: These, friends, are not your ordinary pork chops. In fact, our chefs gave ’em a steak-like treatment, transforming the everyday protein into something extraordinary. The tender chops are coated in steak spice, seared, then drizzled with a creamy shallot pan sauce. Like any great steakhouse-style meal you'd eat with a date, the sides are just as impressive. Roasted potatoes and zesty green beans round everything out. Now all you need is someone to bring you a dessert menu!
